76
00:12:26,563 --> 00:12:30,286
First, my name.

77
00:12:30,366 --> 00:12:31,307
My name is Mark Rumley.

78
00:12:31,327 --> 00:12:32,288
I'm the city solicitor.

79
00:12:32,308 --> 00:12:35,371
I reside at 50 Woodrow Avenue in Medford.

80
00:12:37,737 --> 00:12:45,463
right now the way the state statute is, and you have to understand this in terms of state statute and local ordinance.

81
00:12:46,023 --> 00:12:50,626
The state statute says in terms of notice that it should be given to

82
00:12:51,969 --> 00:13:01,197
abutters to a petitioner property or abutters to abutters or those who are across the street within a 300-foot ambit.

83
00:13:01,658 --> 00:13:07,703
Now that doesn't mean under the state statute that everybody within the 300-foot ambit would receive notice.

84
00:13:08,083 --> 00:13:11,606
It just means abutters, abutters to abutters or those across the street.

85
00:13:13,553 --> 00:13:28,326
The resolution which is before you tonight would make it a requirement that locally, that in the city of Medford, notice be given to all persons, all persons, within a 400-foot ambit.

86
00:13:29,287 --> 00:13:35,313
Now, it's important to be cognizant of the fact that this is

87
00:13:36,972 --> 00:13:39,954
in excess of what's required by the state statute.

88
00:13:40,454 --> 00:13:45,317
Therefore, from a legal point of view, it would be considered directory only.

89
00:13:45,337 --> 00:13:46,678
I want to give you an example.

90
00:13:47,378 --> 00:13:48,399
The example would be this.

91
00:13:49,099 --> 00:14:03,168
If you were somebody who was, say, 300 feet away, but you were not an abutter or an abutter to an abutter or across the street, and you disagreed with a decision made by the board,

92
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:14,588
If you appealed it, the land court would not recognize the fact that you didn't get notice because you were 300 feet away, because that's a local rule.

93
00:14:15,869 --> 00:14:20,272
So the land court would not say that that would give you the status of a party in interest.

94
00:14:20,532 --> 00:14:22,494
You would have to establish that another way.

95
00:14:23,154 --> 00:14:31,200
So when I say that the extra notice would be directory only, it doesn't mean that it wouldn't be given, because if you pass it as an ordinance,

96
00:14:32,041 --> 00:14:35,584
then the board and commission would have to implement that.

97
00:14:36,324 --> 00:14:55,797
However, what I'm saying is that if somebody appealed the decision to the courts, that would not give them an additional leg to stand on or some status that they didn't otherwise have, because the state statute would control as being the only requirement that's compulsory.

98
00:14:56,938 --> 00:15:01,941
So that's essentially what this ordinance would be.

99
00:15:02,361 --> 00:15:15,288
And I have a little bit of data that I didn't have earlier this morning that I received from Mr. McDougal as to what this would mean from a substantive point of view by way of example, which I could give you if you like.

100
00:15:15,968 --> 00:15:16,829
I'll just explain it.

101
00:15:20,693 --> 00:15:25,377
Dennis McDougall is the clerk for the administrator for the ZBA.

102
00:15:25,898 --> 00:15:40,090
And just as an example of what this would mean, there's one project, I won't give the address, it's not that important, but it was the change of a property from a single family to a two family.

103
00:15:40,110 --> 00:15:41,632
It was before the Board of Appeals.

104
00:15:42,532 --> 00:15:50,961
Under the state statute, which means abutters, abutters to abutters, or those across the street, there were 10 notices that were given out.

105
00:15:52,568 --> 00:16:03,217
If it were all owners within 300 feet, there were 234 people that would have to be notified because there was a condominium within that area.

106
00:16:04,298 --> 00:16:11,465
If it were 400 feet, there'd be 357 people that would have had to have been notified because of that condominium.

107
00:16:12,145 --> 00:16:14,888
Now, that's a very steep example.

108
00:16:15,508 --> 00:16:22,298
There's another one where, on a matter before the ZBA, under the law, 18 people were notified.

109
00:16:23,039 --> 00:16:26,784
If the circle was drawn at 300 feet, 38 people would be notified.

110
00:16:26,864 --> 00:16:28,506
And at 400 feet, 60 people would be notified.

111
00:16:33,596 --> 00:16:40,560
So you can see how there's an additional notice requirement if you draw the circle further out and further out.

112
00:16:40,640 --> 00:16:41,720
That's how this would work.

113
00:16:42,361 --> 00:16:48,564
So I give that to you simply for your information, but that's how this would work.

114
00:16:48,784 --> 00:16:52,987
And the condominium example is steep because obviously there are many units in a condominium.

115
00:16:54,968 --> 00:16:55,248
Thank you.

