125
00:17:35,236 --> 00:17:36,157
Is it enforceable?

126
00:17:36,557 --> 00:17:38,537
So the answer to that question is split.

127
00:17:39,057 --> 00:17:46,159
The first part of the answer is, if it's made an ordinance, then it is required that it be implemented by the local board or commission.

128
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:57,068
However, at the state level, if there was an appeal to the courts, it would be informational but not required.

129
00:17:57,649 --> 00:18:01,653
So to the degree that you would think that the state would enforce it, it would not.

130
00:18:05,835 --> 00:18:11,058
