1378
02:06:50,122 --> 02:06:52,544
Hello, I'm Neil Nunes with the BBC News.

1379
02:06:53,145 --> 02:07:01,312
Results are keenly awaited in Alabama, a traditionally Republican state where votes are being counted in the election for a new U.S.

1380
02:07:01,372 --> 02:07:02,433
Senate representative.

1381
02:07:02,893 --> 02:07:10,579
President Trump's favorite candidate, Roy Moore, is hoping to secure victory and brush off allegations of sexual misconduct with teenagers.

1382
02:07:11,000 --> 02:07:13,902
