1400
02:08:57,990 --> 02:09:11,803
The United Nations Children's Fund, UNICEF, has warned that more than 400,000 severely malnourished children under the age of five in the Democratic Republic of Congo could die within months without emergency intervention.

1401
02:09:12,444 --> 02:09:21,413
UNICEF said the crisis unfolding in the region of Kasai was due to a combination of violence, mass displacement of families, and slumping agricultural output.

1402
02:09:22,013 --> 02:09:30,258
Jose Barahona, Oxfam's director for the country, says a lack of resources is making it difficult to offer help to people in many villages.

1403
02:09:30,878 --> 02:09:34,800
Where we are, this is a very real picture of the situations we face.

1404
02:09:34,820 --> 02:09:36,961
These people have not received anything.

1405
02:09:37,001 --> 02:09:37,602
They are hungry.

1406
02:09:37,902 --> 02:09:38,902
They have huge problems.

1407
02:09:38,922 --> 02:09:40,663
They are asking us desperately for help.

1408
02:09:41,223 --> 02:09:44,305
We have some resources that we have already committed in other villages.

1409
02:09:44,845 --> 02:09:46,887
If we want to come here, we need extra resources.

1410
02:09:47,507 --> 02:09:48,668
World News from the BBC.

1411
02:09:50,502 --> 02:10:00,207
