1412
02:10:00,747 --> 02:10:10,671
Mr. Guterres told more than 50 heads of state gathered at the One Planet Summit in Paris, we are in a war for the very existence of life on our planet as we know it.

1413
02:10:11,932 --> 02:10:18,718
Scientists say the region around the North Pole shows no sign of returning to its once reliably frozen state.

1414
02:10:19,259 --> 02:10:20,960
The annual assessment by the U.S.

1415
02:10:21,020 --> 02:10:30,229
National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration says the rapidly warming Arctic indicates that its environmental system has reached a new normal.

1416
02:10:30,649 --> 02:10:31,530
Here's Victoria Gill.

1417
02:10:32,180 --> 02:10:45,452
While this past summer in the far north was cooler than in recent years, average air and sea surface temperatures continued to increase and the winter sea ice maximum, measured by satellites in March, was the lowest on record.

1418
02:10:46,033 --> 02:10:48,375
As the ice melts, the region is darkening.

1419
02:10:48,815 --> 02:10:54,040
Those white reflective surfaces are giving way to reveal darker earth and ocean beneath.

1420
02:10:54,480 --> 02:10:56,622
which absorb even more of the sun's energy.

1421
02:10:56,642 --> 02:11:02,588
The constantly and reliably frozen north, scientists say, could now be a relic of the past.

1422
02:11:03,449 --> 02:11:09,074
An explosion at a plant in Austria has interrupted the flow of gas from Russia to Italy.

1423
02:11:09,414 --> 02:11:13,858
