1426
02:11:25,667 --> 02:11:30,950
In a study, the bees were given the task of finding the most efficient routes between different sources of food.

1427
02:11:31,350 --> 02:11:36,433
They were also tempting traps thrown in to trick them into increasing the distance they travelled.

1428
02:11:36,853 --> 02:11:44,977
At first, the bees fell for the inducement, but then, far from bumbling, they learned to refine their flight paths between flower feeding stations.

1429
02:11:46,038 --> 02:11:47,899
That's the latest BBC News.

1430
02:11:50,278 --> 02:11:52,919
You're listening to the Newsroom from the BBC World Service.

1431
02:11:53,119 --> 02:11:59,880
