1432
02:12:00,261 --> 02:12:07,062
The Republican candidate, Roy Moore, who's denied accusations of child abuse, has been publicly endorsed by the US president.

1433
02:12:07,502 --> 02:12:14,724
The Democratic Party hasn't won in the state in more than two decades, but many think its candidate, Doug Jones, has a real chance.

1434
02:12:15,184 --> 02:12:17,705
From Birmingham in Alabama, Nick Bryant reports.

1435
02:12:18,567 --> 02:12:25,093
Just when he thought that American politics couldn't get any weirder, Judge Roy Moore arrived to vote on horseback.

1436
02:12:27,254 --> 02:12:30,857
