1437
02:12:31,258 --> 02:12:36,242
To his female accusers, he's a sexual predator who molested teenage girls in his 30s.

1438
02:12:36,562 --> 02:12:43,668
To his fans, he's a crusading conservative evangelical, a firebrand populist in the mold of Donald Trump.

1439
02:12:44,148 --> 02:12:45,630
I want to make America great again.

1440
02:12:46,720 --> 02:12:47,743
with President Trump.

1441
02:12:48,345 --> 02:12:52,216
I want America great, but I want America good, and she can't be good

1442
02:12:53,782 --> 02:12:54,902
until we go back to God.

1443
02:12:55,242 --> 02:13:01,344
