1444
02:13:01,804 --> 02:13:03,085
They're crying fake news.

1445
02:13:03,425 --> 02:13:05,345
That's nothing but a bunch of fake news.

1446
02:13:05,725 --> 02:13:07,826
And they've already been proven false.

1447
02:13:07,886 --> 02:13:10,727
If they were really true, why didn't they come out before now?

1448
02:13:10,867 --> 02:13:22,470
Though many senior Republicans have refused to back Moore, including Alabama's highly respected Senator Richard Shelby, he has a cheerleader in Donald Trump, who's made automated calls on his behalf.

1449
02:13:22,810 --> 02:13:27,873
Hi, this is President Donald Trump, and I need Alabama to go vote for Roy Moore.

1450
02:13:28,193 --> 02:13:29,634
It is so important.

1451
02:13:29,774 --> 02:13:32,076
For the president, it's morally uncomplicated.

1452
02:13:32,296 --> 02:13:35,938
He wants Alabama to send a Republican, not a Democrat, to the Senate.

1453
02:13:36,699 --> 02:13:41,722
