1464
02:14:34,721 --> 02:14:36,823
Voted for Rory Moore, Republican.

1465
02:14:37,983 --> 02:14:40,744
I believe that he stands for the values that I was brought up with.

1466
02:14:41,504 --> 02:14:45,765
And I believe that the generation that we're in right now, we need a lot of more.

1467
02:14:46,505 --> 02:14:51,486
I voted for him because I believe he believes in the right thing and he also believes in God.

1468
02:14:52,287 --> 02:14:57,428
